Document: LinkButton
Path: godot/classes/class_linkbutton.rst
Summary: This section details the properties available for configuring a LinkButton, including text, language, URI, and text rendering behaviors.

ellipsis_char (String): Ellipsis character used for text clipping. Default: "…"
Method: set_ellipsis_char(value: String)
Method: get_ellipsis_char()

language (String): Language code used for line-breaking and text shaping algorithms. If left empty, the current locale is used instead. Default: ""
Method: set_language(value: String)
Method: get_language()

structured_text_bidi_override (StructuredTextParser): Set BiDi algorithm override for the structured text. Default: 0
Method: set_structured_text_bidi_override(value: StructuredTextParser)
Method: get_structured_text_bidi_override()

structured_text_bidi_override_options (Array): Set additional options for BiDi override. Default: []
Method: set_structured_text_bidi_override_options(value: Array)
Method: get_structured_text_bidi_override_options()

text (String): The button's text that will be displayed inside the button's area. Default: ""
Method: set_text(value: String)
Method: get_text()

text_direction (TextDirection): Base text writing direction. Default: 0
Method: set_text_direction(value: TextDirection)
Method: get_text_direction()

text_overrun_behavior (OverrunBehavior): Sets the clipping behavior when the text exceeds the node's bounding rectangle. Default: 0
Method: set_text_overrun_behavior(value: OverrunBehavior)
Method: get_text_overrun_behavior()

underline (UnderlineMode): The underline mode to use for the text. Default: 0
Method: set_underline_mode(value: UnderlineMode)
Method: get_underline_mode()

uri (String): The URI for this LinkButton. If set to a valid URI, pressing the button opens the URI using the operating system's default program for the protocol (via OS.shell_open). HTTP and HTTPS URLs open the default web browser. Default: ""
Method: set_uri(value: String)
Method: get_uri()

GDScript:
uri = "https://godotengine.org" # Opens the URL in the default web browser.
uri = "C:\SomeFolder" # Opens the file explorer at the given path.
uri = "C:\SomeImage.png" # Opens the given image in the default viewing app.

C#:
Uri = "https://godotengine.org"; // Opens the URL in the default web browser.
Uri = "C:\SomeFolder"; // Opens the file explorer at the given path.
Uri = "C:\SomeImage.png"; // Opens the given image in the default viewing app.
